dct_title_s: Humboldt County, California GIS Maps & Data
dct_description_sm: This collection of data is produced by the Humboldt County Planning and Building Department. Data layers in this collection cover a variety of themes, including: parcels. boundaries, zoning, physical features, land use, transportation, public safety, and utilities. These data were downloaded from the Humboldt County GIS Data Download site (http://humboldtgov.org/276/GIS-Data-Download) on October 5, 2015.
System requirements: Geographic Information Systems (GIS) software that reads ESRI shapefile format.
dct_publisher_sm: County of Humboldt Planning and Building Department
